(228, 1, '2021-04-03 20:17:43', '2021-04-03 23:17:43', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":217,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-36-1024x620.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-217\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Certa vez enquanto estudava a respeito de rodar ragnarok via navegador vi a necessidade de criar um app que reunisse o maximo de ferramentas em um unico local e que fosse possivel usar pelo celular, foi então que criei o App RagTools (atualmente perdido na net), tempo se passou e cheguei na faculdade e no semestre comecei a aprender C#, foi então que tive a ideia de rafazer este app, mas dessa vez como um programa para Windows, com diversas funcionalidades novas, algumas das funcionalidades antigas infelizmente não puderam ser mantidas (#RIPCronusEmulator).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>ScreenShots</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Menu Principal</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":218,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-37.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-218\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Ferramentas Online</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":219,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-38.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-219\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Sprites ID</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":220,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-39-1024x584.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-220\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Simuladores</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":221,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-40-1024x590.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-221\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Database OldSchool</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":222,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-41-1024x589.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-222\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Database Renewal</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":223,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-42-1024x586.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-223\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Conteudo Adicional</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":224,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-43-1024x588.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-224\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Ferramentas Offline</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":225,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-44.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-225\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Créditos</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":226,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-45.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-226\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Sobre</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":227,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-46.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-227\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Caso queira Visualizar os arquivos desse projeto <a href=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/files/#files%2FRagTools\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/files/#files%2FRagTools\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Clique Aqui</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'RagTools', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '216-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-04-03 20:17:43', '2021-04-03 23:17:43', '', 216, 'http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/?p=228', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(229, 1, '2021-04-03 20:26:02', '2021-04-03 23:26:02', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":232,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-49-1024x642.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-232\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Uma vez na faculdade durante uma aula chata fiz um programa em C que gerava a tabuada de acordo com as necessidades de quem utiliza podendo escolher o limite de geração da tabuada.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Caso queira visualizar essa versão <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://replit.com/@angelusinferni/tabuada\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://replit.com/@angelusinferni/tabuada\" target=\"_blank\">Clique Aqui</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tempos depois na faculdade foram introduzidas aulas de C#, foi então que me perguntei se eu era capaz de converter manualmente um programa que era originalmente feito em C para C# com interface grafica.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>E não foi que eu consegui !</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":231,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/image-48-1024x619.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-231\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Caso queira visualizar os arquivos desse projeto <a href=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/files/#files%2FTabuada\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http://kmc.rf.gd/files/#files%2FTabuada\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Clique Aqui</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Tabuada', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tabuada', '', '', '2021-04-03 20:26:02', '2021-04-03 23:26:02', '', 0, 'http://kmc.rf.gd/aio/?p=229', 0, 'post', '', 0),
